				<td colspan="2"><span>My main is a 65 mage, and I dual box a 61 bard (which I greatly enjoy, and if it was flagged, would probably be my main). I wanted to try aggro kiting with the bard and the mage, and have tried straight chanting down a mob with water pet BS'ing it. Even if I wait until the target mob is down to 70% or so, the water pet (with taunt off) will grab aggro at about 20%. Any suggestions for a song lineup that will help the bard maintain aggro throughout a kite (and perhaps get the pet in their earlier)?
<br />
